  <li><strong>Updated â€œMake it goâ€ based on instructions by Jas Strong</strong> (She has a video at http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yEfToeTW8rU ).  These work for the Ensemble RX II, which tunes from broadcast AM radio to about 30 Mhz.
